{"tid":1886953,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"ff系列 - 深水埗搞康健中心","createTime":"2020-02-19T08:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T05:18:57.000Z","uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0c125d962202e393332007ee8db2c223f7a4d939","tid":1886953,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:53:54.000Z","msg":"有冇yoyo想還拖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>深水埗和黃大仙地區康健中心營運服務招標期延長<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  食物及衞生局今日（二月十七日）宣布，提供深水埗和黃大仙地區康健中心營運服務的招標期延長至四月二十四日中午十二時。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote> 地區康健中心營運者透過醫社合作和公私合營的模式提供由政府補貼的基層醫療服務，包括健康推廣、健康評估、慢性疾病管理和社區復康，藉以提升市民的自我管理健康能力，並為長期病患者在社區內提供支援。</blockquote><br />\n健康推廣、健康評估=大量cc台分析師<br />\n慢性疾病管理=賭波賭馬yoyo，包你慢慢冇病變有病<br />\n社區復康=去家興掃貨爭紙皮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KRpohn4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKRpohn4.gif&h=eb4bdb89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n通州街玩BB彈槍<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/A2E0w_T3pheTmuhuVePRPg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/onccinstantnews.com/f1bd8157ea24ef5a1a8b5dfa86e2aec6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FA2E0w_T3pheTmuhuVePRPg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Ff1bd8157ea24ef5a1a8b5dfa86e2aec6&h=f538a954&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n爭櫈仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.litenews.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/2001211.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.litenews.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F2001211.jpg&h=19cb82ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>我們會研究於地區康健中心為巿民接種流感疫苗。</blockquote><br />\n有N賓乜針都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇清john?<br />\n利申ff緊"},{"pid":"1e393a5d50876d518ac63f78dc755cc98a1a9fe0","tid":1886953,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191207/_2019120713040938537.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191207%2F_2019120713040938537.jpg&h=6b387fca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n計劃中的地區康健中心則設於石硤尾邨第六期(美禧樓及美柏樓)二樓。"},{"pid":"1761d21163f012c83ef273761ecea7168a517711","tid":1886953,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:55:35.000Z","msg":"收費方面，諮詢服務完全免費，診症診金政府則每次資助250元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，如果醫生收費高於政府資助額，病人便要自付當中的差額。康健中心提供的物理治療、中醫針灸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等服務，每次收費100至150元。中心亦有健康舞、瑜珈班，經治療師評估後，有需要人士可免費參加。"},{"pid":"0c95331da0480bd335509fb656b406f3e2f4a64d","tid":1886953,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:52:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://whatsticker.online/stickers_asset/ws-pack-256475N6kuN3E/c6e50e4eaed6.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwhatsticker.online%2Fstickers_asset%2Fws-pack-256475N6kuN3E%2Fc6e50e4eaed6.webp&h=9682b66e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9a12d585423b5f48cc5494f5b72ca69e40a3c1d","tid":1886953,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6305884bcc330ccc3f5db7f8e135c56acd0116c","tid":1886953,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4630504c1874ff96064d6e5b60f4cf3228457fd3","tid":1886953,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6305884bcc330ccc3f5db7f8e135c56acd0116c","tid":1886953,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/c